'''Slate Star Codex''' (abbreviated '''SSC''') is a blog by Scott Alexander.<ref name="about_page">{{cite web |url=http://slatestarcodex.com/about/ |author=Scott Alexander |title=About |date=January 26, 2016 |publisher=Slate Star Codex |accessdate=February 11, 2017}}</ref> The rationality community thinks it's [[wiktionary:overrated|pretty good]].

==Scope and aims==

{{as of|2017|02}}, Scott Alexander describes SSC as "a blog about science, medicine, philosophy, politics, and futurism".<ref name="about_page" />

mention discussion threads

==Name==

The name of the blog, "Slate Star Codex", is an approximate anagram of "Scott Alexander".<ref>{{cite web |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213030030/http://slatestarcodex.com/about/ |title=About |author=Scott Alexander |publisher=Slate Star Codex |accessdate=February 19, 2017 |quote="Slate Star Codex" is a slant anagram of my name.}}</ref>

